entry.def: Something that is rounded is curved in shape, without any points or sharp edges.

example.ex: The barge had a rounded bow and stern.
example.tran: 这艘驳船的两端都是圆形的。

entry.tran: 全面发展的;多方面的;完善的
entry.def: You describe something or someone as rounded or well-rounded when you are expressing approval of them because they have a personality which is fully developed in all aspects.

example.ex: ...his carefully organised narrative, full of rounded, believable and interesting characters.
example.tran: 他的叙述结构严谨，不乏形象丰满、真实有趣的人物

example.ex: ...a well-rounded, well-educated and highly intelligent man...
example.tran: 全面发展、受过良好教育的聪明过人的男子
